# CheckboxChipGroup

A set of options presented as chips with multiple options to select.

If you need to allow selecting only one option, consider using [<mark>`RadioChipGroup`</mark>]({base}/docs/components/radio-chip-group). If you need more customization for the chips, such as their slots, take a look at [<mark>`CheckboxChip`</mark>]({base}/docs/components/checkbox-chip), the building block of this component.

